              },
              "free_text": [
                " Pelletron Laboratory of the University",
                "of Sao Paulo"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "An isotopically enriched Mg-24 target, evaporated in",
                "C-12 backing, were used.",
                "For normalization purposes, a 1 mug/cm**2 thick gold",
                "layer was evaporated on the targets."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "PROPC",
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Three sets of delta-E-E telescopes",
                "were used, the E detector was standard Si surface",
                "barrier  detectors, the delta-E detectors proportional",
                "counters for the forward angles and surface barrier",
                "detectors for the backward angle data.",
                "A monitor detector placed at 15-degree with respect",
                "to the beam permitted to calculated the ratio of Mg-24",
                "to gold target thicknesses."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The absolute cross sections were obtained",
                "by normalizing to Rutherford scattering on gold and",
                "using the ratio of target thicknesses. The energy",
                "resolution at all angles was sufficient to separate",
                "the elastic peal from inelastic peaks."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".Optical model and closed-formalism parameters.",
                "A typical proton spectrum of C-12 ions elastically",
                "scattered at Ang(lab)=40 degree and spectra of O-16",
                "originating from the Mg-24(6-C-12,O-16)Ne-20(g.s)",
                "transfer reaction were obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The absolute errors in the elastic cross section are 5%",
                "for the forward angles and 10-20% for intermediate",
                "angles."
              ]
            },
